&lt;h1 id="why-you-need-to-be-in-silicon-valley"&gt;Why You Need to be in Silicon Valley&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jan 17 2010&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For years I didn&amp;rsquo;t believe this. I thought that you could take advantage of the benefits of Boston, Seattle, NY, Austin – cheaper talent, no echo chamber, local Universities, etc.. But I give up. I found myself telling an entrepreneur why he had to be in Silicon Valley if he wanted to succeed. Most of my points are about Consumer Internet businesses&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>